beer.beer_description:
Can you sense the subtle and refreshing fruity aroma? Your senses are not deceiving you. is wheat beer brewed the traditional way from wheat and barley malt is distinctive for its particularly gourmet aroma. Creamy-textured, light, somewhat sweetish Vilkmerges WHEAT BEER has a cloudy, almost white colour. Before pouring the beer into a glass, in the bottle to stir up the yeast sediment. As you smell its aroma and savour the first sip, you will taste a subtle but unforgettable aftertaste of citrus fruit and spices, which is unlike anything else. It makes our beer unique. 
The beer got GOLD medal in Lithuanian competition „Best product 2012“ of Lithuania (“Metų gaminys“).

Try 5 more for Level 2!
